Introduction

CSR (Cheot-Sarang) meaning "first love," is a South Korean girl group under A2Z Entertainment. The group consists of seven members: Geumhee, Sihyeon, Seoyeon, Yuna, Duna, Sua, and Yeham.

Their concept is a class of girls all born in 2005. They used to be called "05class" but ultimately changed their name to CSR.

The group made it's official debut on July 27, 2022 with the mini album "Sequence: 7272".
